DeMint Says Obama Deficit Plan ‘Just for Politics’

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-20T13:41:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/demint-says-obama-deficit-plan-just-for-politics-video.html
Sen. James DeMint, a Republican 
from  South Carolina , discusses President  Barack Obama 's 
deficit-reduction plan.  DeMint, speaking with  Peter Cook  on Bloomberg Television's 
"In the Loop," also says Federal Reserve Chairman Ben S. 
Bernanke needs to "stop trying to micro-manage our economy." 
(Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 03:20
 